      <title>大厅说，德国债务方案增加了10亿欧元的银行收入。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/german-debt-package-to-add-1-billion-bank-revenue-lobby-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政府计划增加国防和基础设施支出的计划，德国的金融业每年将获得10亿欧元（11亿美元）的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/german-debt-package-to-add-1-billion-bank-revenue-lobby-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 08:27:16 GMT</pubDate>
