    <item>
      <title>EuroNext首席执行官说，投资者因不确定性从我们身上撤出了黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/euronext-ceo-says-investors-pull-gold-out-of-us-over-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Euronext NV首席执行官Stephane Boujnah表示，一些欧洲投资者对特朗普政府的贸易政策感到不安，以至于他们开始将黄金从美国移出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/euronext-ceo-says-investors-pull-gold-out-of-us-over-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 08:13:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝特尔：如果欧盟联合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-08/bettel-can-strike-compromise-on-tariffs-if-eu-united-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢森堡副总理和外交大臣Xavier Bettel表示，只要所有成员国团结在一起，欧洲就可以在与美国的贸易冲突中找到解决方案。

贝特尔周一在卢森堡举行的欧盟贸易部长会议上与彭博的奥利弗·克鲁克（Oliver Crook）进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-08/bettel-can-strike-compromise-on-tariffs-if-eu-united-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 08:12:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保时捷中国销售低迷，关税蒙蔽前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/porsche-global-sales-drop-led-by-declines-in-china-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保时捷AG的中国销售量在十多年来跌至最低，这进一步掩盖了豪华汽车制造商的前景，因为新的美国关税威胁到其最大的市场上的订单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/porsche-global-sales-drop-led-by-declines-in-china-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在“极端”情况下，高盛警告以低于$ 40的油。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/goldman-says-oil-could-sink-below-40-under-extreme-conditions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团公司＆Mdash;一周内两次切割油预测及其刚开始切油。说，随着贸易战争的爆发和供应的增长，布伦特在“极端”结果下有可能以每桶40美元的价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/goldman-says-oil-could-sink-below-40-under-extreme-conditions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 05:23:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
